snippet.textDisplay: I heard this song multiple times and still think of listening it again and again. I always have mixed emotion. I don't understand who divided us on the basis of religion and why was it necessary. Because of a handful of bloody politicians we got divided and the bloody game is still on. I would request people of both countries to be very sensible while electing their leaders who can lead them towards prosperity and peacefulness. This song binds people of India and Pakistan together. I salute you for composing and singing this song. Musicians have also played a very pivotal role in giving the sound effects which directly touches the heart.
